#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.24:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.24:0.2"
msgid "3. Chaḷindriyavagga"
msgstr "3. The Six Faculties"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 24. Ekabījīsutta → ekābhiññaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Ekabījīsutta"
msgstr "24. A One-Seeder"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.205"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.24:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, indriyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five faculties."

msgctxt "sn48.24:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn48.24:1.3"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ—"
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.24:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcindriyāni."
msgstr "These are the five faculties."

#. VAR: ekabījī → ekabīji (mr)
#. VAR: sattakkhattuparamo → sattakkhattuṃparamo (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn48.24:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ samattā paripūrattā arahaṃ hoti, "
"tato mudutarehi antarāparinibbāyī hoti, tato mudutarehi upahaccaparinibbāyī "
"hoti, tato mudutarehi asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti, tato mudutarehi "
"sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti, tato mudutarehi uddhaṃsoto hoti akaniṭṭhagāmī, "
"tato mudutarehi sakadāgāmī hoti, tato mudutarehi ekabījī hoti, tato "
"mudutarehi kolaṃkolo hoti, tato mudutarehi sattakkhattuparamo hoti, tato "
"mudutarehi dhammānusārī hoti, tato mudutarehi saddhānusārī hotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Someone who has completed and fulfilled these five faculties is a perfected "
"one. If they are weaker than that, they’re one who is extinguished in-"
"between one life and the next … one who is extinguished upon landing … one "
"who is extinguished without extra effort … one who is extinguished with "
"extra effort … one who heads upstream, going to the Akaniṭṭha realm … a once-"
"returner … a one-seeder … one who goes from family to family … one who has "
"seven rebirths at most … a follower of the teachings … a follower by faith.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.24:1.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
